snippet: Novak Djokovic and Serena Williams faced what were supposed to be their biggest challenges to date at this year's Australian Open on Tuesday but both rattled off comfortable victories to march into the semi-finals....
lead_paragraph: Novak Djokovic and Serena Williams faced what were supposed to be their biggest challenges to date at this year's Australian Open on Tuesday but both rattled off comfortable victories to march into the semi-finals.

headline.print_headline: Easy Does It as Djokovic, Serena Reach Last Four
headline.main: Easy Does It as Djokovic, Serena Reach Last Four
